{"tid":285362,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iphone隻火牛入左水點搞","createTime":"2017-06-15T17:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T20:09:11.000Z","uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"885b9ceeae379dfd807e61e98a657d3863b4f446","tid":285362,"uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"呢幾日去左台灣旅行<br />\n大雨到仆街，個袋濕撚晒<br />\n攞隻牛出黎叉果時醒唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叉左幾秒部機都冇反應<br />\n點知叉叉下隻牛有水滴出黎<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時隻牛叉電都熱熱地，應該係入面水滾所以必返啲水出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我又開唔到隻牛黎搞，點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說如果我掂到啲水係咪死撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667a14a132871cf2e4e143de8a7a9bcd76a3e997","tid":285362,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:43:39.000Z","msg":"你拎隻牛送比仇人都得，爆硬"},{"pid":"5d66f147febebd6502dd082eaed431db0f55605e","tid":285362,"uid":9338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:44:42.000Z","msg":"買過隻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba978764065ae6ea999a22595433179a76b774c","tid":285362,"uid":8718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:45:17.000Z","msg":"買過隻囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以點<br />\n再唔係咪拎去天材吧整 配件好似包半年<br />\n但你人為都唔知點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以都係買過隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc47ae8e6299d88a08aa1f4ed8f6f62c6fc73bd","tid":285362,"uid":62384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:47:19.000Z","msg":"咁都要問<br />\n智商應該低過80"},{"pid":"4dc72560ef2c7842581f80f112b14c80fb3557d9","tid":285362,"uid":8718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都要問<br />\n智商應該低過80</blockquote><br />\n可能期待有連登仔識隔空幫佢整番好隻火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c700994de5b1a46d58962ec795195705e7e6f86e","tid":285362,"uid":28059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:50:45.000Z","msg":"火牛應該無試水紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等佢乾左拎去apple store 應該得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4082384e3b0cf6cd9ab8de7b2a32dcff33af742d","tid":285362,"uid":19970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:51:42.000Z","msg":"變水牛"},{"pid":"e9773486f29dac70b9bf53caf79cce7cde676233","tid":285362,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:09:11.000Z","msg":"火牛變水牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}